%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stephen%20Colbert's%20'The%20Late%20Show'%20on%20CBS%20is%20getting%20canceled.%20Lawmakers%20want%20to%20know%20if%20it's%20because%20of%20his%20political%20views.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stephen%20Colbert%20said%20he%20does%20not%20joke%20about%20other%20people's%20tragedies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6602cb403f923f7dab012df6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStephen%20Colbert's%20'The%20Late%20Show'%20on%20CBS%20is%20getting%20canceled.%3Cp%3EScott%20Kowalchyk%2FCBS%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECBS%20is%20canceling%20its%20most-watched%20talk%20show%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Late%20Show%20With%20Stephen%20Colbert.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20show%2C%20which%20has%20been%20running%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%2C%20will%20end%20in%20May%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECBS%20said%20the%20cancellation%20was%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20a%20financial%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECBS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fthe-late-show-stephen-colbert-end-may-2026%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Late%20Show%20With%20Stephen%20Colbert%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20canceled%20after%20next%20year%2C%20ending%20a%20series%20that%20has%20been%20running%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColbert%20announced%20the%20talk%20show's%20cancellation%20on%20Thursday%20via%20a%20clip%20of%20his%20new%20episode%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDMOhWKsxT_G%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20we%20start%20the%20show%2C%20I%20want%20to%20let%20you%20know%20something%20I%20found%20out%20just%20last%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNext%20year%20will%20be%20our%20last%20season.%20The%20network%20will%20be%20ending%20'The%20Late%20Show'%20in%20May.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20announcement%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20long%20wave%20of%20boos%20from%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColbert%20took%20over%20as%20host%20of%20the%20talk%20show%20previously%20helmed%20by%20David%20Letterman%20in%202015%2C%20and%20has%20been%20running%20it%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20The%20show%20was%20first%20aired%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECBS%20executives%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F07%2F17%2Fbusiness%2Fstephen-colbert-late-show-ending.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20cancellation%20was%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20a%20financial%20decision%20against%20a%20challenging%20backdrop%20in%20late%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20related%20in%20any%20way%20to%20the%20show's%20performance%2C%20content%20or%20other%20matters%20happening%20at%20Paramount%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20to%20the%20NYT%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERatings%20from%20the%20American%20audience%20measurement%20company%2C%20Nielsen%2C%20seen%20by%20several%20news%20outlets%2C%20show%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Late%20Show%26quot%3B%20performed%20well%20in%20its%20timeslot.%20The%20show%20notched%202.417%20million%20viewers%20across%2041%20new%20episodes%2C%20and%20was%20the%20only%20late-night%20show%20to%20gain%20viewers%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20comes%20shortly%20after%20Paramount%2C%20on%20July%201%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-to-pay-16-million-settle-trump-60-minutes-lawsuit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eagreed%20to%20pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20a%20%2416%20million%20settlement%20over%20a%20lawsuit%20the%20president%20filed%20against%20it.%20The%20lawsuit%20accused%20CBS's%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Bdeceptive%20editing%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20interview%20with%20presidential%20rival%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColbert%20referenced%20the%20settlement%20in%20an%20episode%20on%20July%2014%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BA%20Big%20Bribe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20joke%20about%20the%20settlement%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20who%20has%20always%20been%20a%20proud%20employee%20of%20this%20network%2C%20I%20am%20offended%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20anything%20will%20ever%20repair%20my%20trust%20in%20this%20company.%20But%20just%20taking%20a%20stab%20at%20it%2C%20I'd%20say%20%2416%20million%20would%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20have%20sounded%20out%20concerns%20about%20the%20show's%20cancellation%2C%20asking%20CBS%20if%20the%20decision%20was%20political%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Adam%20Schiff%20of%20California%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20comment%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20finished%20taping%20with%20Stephen%20Colbert%20who%20announced%20his%20show%20was%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20Schiff%20wrote%20in%20a%20late%20Thursday%20evening%20X%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSenAdamSchiff%2Fstatus%2F1945991349339042169%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Paramount%20and%20CBS%20ended%20the%20Late%20Show%20for%20political%20reasons%2C%20the%20public%20deserves%20to%20know.%20And%20deserves%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Schiff%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20of%20Massachusetts%20released%20a%20statement%20just%20hours%20after%20the%20cancellation%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCBS%20canceled%20Colbert's%20show%20just%20three%20days%20after%20Colbert%20called%20out%20CBS%20owner%20Paramount%20for%20its%20%2416%20settlement%20with%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deal%20that%20looks%20like%20bribery.%20America%20deserves%20to%20know%20if%20his%20show%20was%20canceled%20for%20political%20r