ong%3EL.L.Bean%20Stonington%20Daily%20Carry%20Work%20Bag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20this%20L.L.Bean%20bag%20is%20a%20little%20more%20tote-y%20than%20briefcase-y%2C%20I%20think%20it%20could%20be%20a%20great%20fit%20for%20a%20user%20more%20concerned%20with%20carrying%20capacity%20than%20traditional%20briefcase%20aesthetics.%20You're%20getting%20a%20nice%20roomy%20main%20compartment%20with%20multiple%20sections%2C%20including%20a%20fleece-lined%20padded%20sleeve%20that%20can%20fit%20laptops%20up%20to%2015%20inches%2C%20and%20four%20additional%20pockets%20(one%20large%20zippered%20option%20and%20three%20smaller%20ones).%20The%20exterior%20features%20two%20side%20pockets%20for%20water%20bottle%20or%20umbrella%20storage%2C%20and%20another%20pair%20of%20open%20sleeves%20for%20quick%20access.%20This%20storage-friendly%20design%20does%20result%20in%20a%20fairly%20bulky%20bag%2C%20though%2C%20and%20while%20the%20heavy-duty%20canvas%20material%20provides%20durability%2C%20its%20floppy%20construction%20has%20a%20hard%20time%20standing%20upright.%20The%20canvas%20shoulder%20strap%20was%20comfortable%20enough%2C%20but%20the%20flat%20leather%20carrying%20handles%20were%20noticeably%20less%20comfortable%20than%20the%20other%20models%20I%20tested%2C%20lacking%20the%20rounded%20shape%20that%20made%20them%20so%20enjoyable%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaddleback%20Leather%20Fourteener%20Thin%20Leather%20Briefcase%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20leather%20briefcase%20has%20a%20compact%2C%20lightweight%20design%20with%20comfortable%20handles%20and%20a%20distinctive%20Indiana%20Jones-style%20aesthetic.%20I%20really%20appreciated%20its%20rigid%20construction%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20stand%20upright%20and%20not%20immediately%20flop%20over%20when%20placed%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20thick%2C%20heavy-duty%20feel%20(and%20smell!)%20of%20the%20leather.%20However%2C%20it%20fell%20short%20in%20a%20few%20areas%2C%20namely%20the%20limited