ting%2C%20the%20somewhat%20stiff%20clasp%20lock%20mechanism%20took%20some%20time%20to%20loosen%20up%20and%20finally%20work%20smoothly%20and%20without%20occasionally%20sticking%20in%20place.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20I%20really%20appreciated%20the%20variety%20of%20storage%20elements%20inside%2C%20with%20multiple%20full-length%20compartments%2C%20zippered%20pockets%2C%20and%20three%20elastic%20pen%20holders.%20While%20undeniably%20handsome%20and%20built%20to%20last%2C%20its%20weight%20and%20slower%20accessibility%20make%20it%20better%20suited%20for%20users%20who%20prioritize%20classic%20style%20and%20security%20over%20quick%2C%20lightweight%20functionality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20each%20briefcase%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stuart%20%26amp%3B%20Lau%20Cary%20Briefcase%20inside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877eeebf748d8c055f5bb86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20identify%20the%20best%20briefcases%20for%20different%20professional%20needs%2C%20budgets%2C%20and%20lifestyles%2C%20I%20conducted%20extensive%20hands-on%20testing%20of%207%20models%20across%20various%20price%20points%20and%20design%20types.%20Using%20the%20following%20criteria%2C%20my%20comprehensive%20evaluation%20included%20both%20objective%20measurements%20and%20subjective%20assessments%20of%20real-world%20performance.%20Here's%20how%20I%20put%20my%20testing%20pool%20through%20its%20paces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c69be02-12c7-4680-a5cf-a97f9f26b17e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDaily%20Use%20Simulation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20my%20testing%20with%20real-world%20usage%20scenarios%2C%20using%20each%20briefcase%20to%20transport%20my%20laptop%20and%20work%20materials%20during%20daily%20commutes%20to%20and%20from%20my%20home.%20For%20consistency%2C%20I%20loaded%20each%20case%20with%20identical%20items%3A%20a%2013.3-inch%20laptop%2C%20documents%2C%20notebooks%2C%20pens%2C%20charging%20cables%2C%20and%20other%20typical%20work%20essentials.%20Each%20briefcase%20was%20carried%20for%20at%20least%2030%20minutes%20of%20walking%20per%20day%20over%20multiple%20testing%20sessions%2C%20with%20each%20case%20opened%20and%20closed%20a%20minimum%20of%2015%20times%20throughout%20each%20testing%20day.%20During%20this%20process%2C%20I%20evaluated%20ease%20of%20access%20to%20contents%2C%20comfort%20during%20extended%20carrying%20periods%2C%20stability%20when%20placed%20on%20various%20surfaces%2C%20and%20monitored%20for%20any%20signs%20of%20early%20wear%20or%20structural%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1eaf583-cafa-48cf-8779-cc3a5a970e7d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsability%20and%20Access%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20use%20case%20or%20setting%2C%20the%20convenience%20of%20operation%20is%20important%20for%20any%20briefcase.%20I%20tested%20each%20model's%20opening%20and%20closing%20mechanisms%20extensively%2C%20evaluating%20whether%20zippers%2C%20clasps%2C%20buckles%2C%20and%20flaps%20operated%20smoothly%20or%20presented%20frustrating%20obstacles%20(noting%20any%20issues%20like%20sharp%20zippers%20rubbing%20against%20my%20skin%20or%20dark%20interiors%20that%20are%20difficult%20to%20see%20into).%20I%20assessed%20how%20quickly%20and%20easily%20I%20could%20access%20items%20stored%20in%20different%20compartments%2C%20noting%20whether%20the%20interior%20organization%20facilitated%20efficient%20retrieval%20or%20required%20digging%20through%20large%20compartments%20or%20struggling%20to%20see%20in%20low-light%20conditions.%20I%20also%20evaluated%20whether%20each%20briefcase%20could%20be%20opened%20and%20accessed%20while%20holding%20them%20(both%20by%20handles%20or%20shoulder%20straps)%2C%20if%20they%20required%20placement%20on%20a%20surface%20to%20operate%20effectively%2C%20or%20were%20rigid%20enough%20to%20stand%20upright%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e953a1b-416f-4fa9-9834-45b1825e6aab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrganization%20and%20Storage%20Capacity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20logged%20the%20organizational%20features%20of%20each%20briefcase%2C%20counting%20and%20measuring%20all%20compartments%2C%20pockets%2C%20and%20specialized%20storage%20areas%20in%20order%20to%20confidently%20evaluate%20one%20versus%20another.%20I%20tested%20how%20well%20each%20case%20accommodated%20different%20types%20and%20sizes%20of%20items%2C%20from%20laptops%20and%20tablets%20to%20documents%2C%20business%20cards%2C%20and%20smaller%20accessories.%20For%20laptop%20compartments%2C%20I%20measured%20maximum%20device%20dimensions%20that%20could%20fit%20comfortably%20and%20tested%20with%20various%20laptop%20sizes%20(both%2013.3%20and%2016%20inches)%20to%20determine%20true%20capacity%20limits.%20I%20also%20evaluated%20the%20accessibility%20and%20practicality%20of%20exterior%20pockets%20for%20items%20requiring%20quick%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6fbc31a-0f3b-43b1-9f21-3414b9879148%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%20Quality%20and%20Durability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20evaluate%20build%20quality%20and%20long-term%20durability%2C%20I%20conducted%20both%20visual%20inspections%20and%20stress%20tests.%20I%20examined%20the%20materials%20used%20throughout%20each%20briefcase%2C%20identifying%20leather%20types%20(full-grain%2C%20top-grain%2C%20or%20bonded)%2C%20fabric%20qualities%2C%20and%20hardware%20construction.%20I%20performed%20aggressive%20handling%20tests%2C%20swinging%20each%20fully-loaded%20briefcase%20by%20its%20handles%20and%20straps%20to%20identify%20potential%20failure%20points%20like%20stressed%20seams%2C%20pulled%20stitching%2C%20or%20hardware%20separation.%20I%20also%20tested%20water%20resistance%20by%20applying%20light%20water%20exposure%20to%20small%2C%20inconspicuous%20areas%20and%20evaluating%20how%20well%20different%20materials%20repelled%20moisture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec49b528-c423-4e3d-a118-12b34a69e01a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20Aesthetics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20briefcases%20often%20serve%20as%20professional%20accessories%20that%20reflect%20personal%20style%2C%20I%20assessed%20the%20visual%20appeal%20and%20perceived%20quality%20of%20each%20model.%20I%20evaluated%20whether%20each%20briefcase%20projected%20a%20professional%2C%20high-quality%20appearance%20or%20appeared%20cheap%20and%20poorly%20constructed.%20I%20considered%20factors%20like%20proportions%2C%20color%20options%2C%20hardware%20finish%20quality%2C%20and%20overall%20design%20cohesiveness.%20I%20also%20noted%20how%20each%20briefcase's%20appearance%20held%20up%20after%20extended%20use%20and%20handling.%20Although%20this%20evaluation%20is%20somewhat%20subjective%2C%20it%20did%20help%20me%20better%20identify%20which%20models%20would%20be%20more%20suited%20to%20a%20specific%20wardrobe%2C%20personal%20style%2C%20or%20use%20case%2C%20without%20feeling%20mis-matched%20or%20out%20of%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8241947-845f-4fc9-bfac-00c699819de2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%20and%20Ergonomics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20evaluated%20the%20comfort%20and%20ergonomics%20of%20each%20briefcase's%20carrying%20options%20during%20extended%20use.%20For%20handles%2C%20I%20assessed%20grip%20comfort%2C%20size%20appropriateness%20for%20different%20hand%20sizes%2C%20and%20whether%20extended%20carrying%20caused%20discomfort%20or%20fatigue.%20For%20briefcases%20with%20shoulder%20straps%2C%20I%20tested%20strap%20comfort%2C%20adjustability%2C%20and%20how%20well%20the%20weight%20distributed%20across%20the%20shoulder%20during%20longer%20carrying%20periods%2C%20and%20if%20the%20shoulder%20padding%20provided%20enough%20grip%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20slipping%20off%20my%20shoulder%20while%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226759438b-43b2-4902-b4a9-c2532ccd9c79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdditional%20Performance%20Metrics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20primary%20evaluation%20criteria%2C%20I%20measured%20and%20compared%20several%20additional%20factors%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Using%20precise%20measurements%20and%20a%20luggage%20scale%2C%20I%20documented%20the%20exact%20dimensions%20and%20weight%20of%20each%20while%20empty%2C%20assessing%20how%20compact%20each%20case%20was%20for%20storage%20and%20transport%20convenience.%20The%20ability%20to%20stand%20on%20its%20own%20(or%20at%20least%20not%20completely%20flop%20over)%20factored%20into%20this%20category%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20Features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20noted%20if%20each%20case%20featured%20any%20kind%20of%20locking%20mechanism%2C%20whether%20that%20was%20a%20dedicated%20lock%20and%20key%20on%20the%20main%20compartment%2C%20or%20if%20exterior%20pockets%20provided%20at%20least%20a%20zipper%20or%20magnetic%20closure%20system%20to%20potentially%20deter%20any%20nosy%20passersby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintenance%20Requirements%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20researched%20and%20tested%20cleaning%20procedures%20for%20each%20material%20type%2C%20noting%20whether%20cases%20required%20special%20care%2C%20conditioning%2C%20or%20were%20particularly%20susceptible%20to%20stains%20and%20discoloration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EH%3Cstrong%3Eow%20do%20I%20clean%20and%20maintain%20my%20briefcase%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20the%20type%20of%20material%20used%20in%20its%20construction%2C%20your%20model%20may%20have%20different%20requirements%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20spot%20cleaning%2C%20as%20well%20as%20extending%20its%20overall%20lifespan.%20You%20should%20always%20consult%20the%20specific%20user%20or%20care%20instructions%2C%20but%20as%20a%20general%20rule%2C%20leather%20briefcases%20can%20be%20cleaned%20with%20a%20damp%20cloth%20to%20remove%20surface%20dirt%2C%20with%20leather%20conditioner%20applied%20every%203-6%20months%20to%20prevent%20cracking.%20Use%20leather-specific%20cleaners%20for%20stubborn%20stains%20and%20store%20away%20from%20direct%20sunlight%20and%20extreme%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanvas%20and%20nylon%20briefcases%20can%20typically%20be%20spot-cleaned%20with%20mild%20soap%20and%20water.%20Some%20fabric%20briefcases%20are%20machine%20washable%2C%20just%20check%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%20first%20and%20make%20sure%20to%20remove%20all%20contents%20before%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20briefcase%20types%2C%20try%20to%20empty%20pockets%20regularly%20to%20prevent%20debris%20buildup%2C%20and%20wipe%20down%20hardware%20like%20zippers%20and%20locks%20with%20a%20damp%20cloth%20to%20prevent%20corrosion.%20If%20needed%2C%20lubricate%20zippers%20occasionally%20with%20zipper%20wax%20for%20smooth%20operation.%20When%20not%20in%20use%2C%20store%20briefcases%20in%20cool%2C%20dry%20places%20and%20stuff%20with%20tissue%20paper%20to%20maintain%20shape%20during%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ED%3Cstrong%3Eo%20briefcases%20look%20outdated%20in%20modern%20workplaces%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo!%20Briefcases%20remain%20absolutely%20relevant%20in%20modern%20workplaces%2C%20though%20their%20appropriateness%20depends%20on%20industry%20and%20company%20culture.%20In%20traditional%20professional%20sectors%20like%20law%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20consulting%2C%20briefcases%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20gold%20standard%2C%20projecting%20the%20authority%20and%20competence%20that%20clients%20and%20peers%20expect.%20Senior%20executives%20across%20industries%20typically%20favor%20briefcases%20for%20their%20polished%2C%20established%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20contemporary%20workplaces%20have%20embraced%20casual%20alternatives%20like%20messenger%20bags%2C%20backpacks%2C%20or%20sleek%20laptop%20cases%20that%20align%20with%20informal%20cultures%20and%20offer%20better%20ergonomics%20for%20daily%20commuting%20(those%20classic%20attache%20cases%20aren't%20exactly%20subway%20or%20bike-friendly%2C%20for%20example).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20here%20is%20reading%20your%20workplace%20environment.%20If%20colleagues%20and%20leadership%20carry%20briefcases%2C%20following%20suit%20can%20demonstrate%20a%20proactive%2C%20professional%20awareness.%20Conversely%2C%20a%20traditional%20leather%20attach%C3%A9%20case%20might%20appear%20out%20of%20touch%20in%20a%20more%20casual%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20modern%20briefcase%20designs%20have%20evolved%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%2C%20offering%20slimmer%20profiles%2C%20contemporary%20materials%2C%20and%20hybrid%20functionality%20that%20works%20in%20both%20formal%20and%20casual%20settings%20(I%20think%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110045978xej-20%26h%3Db13063b95d698f433bf8ebc6e38b7bec4784521e9887bf6ee4e3158acf24431d%26postID%3D6877cfb12d2d32d710ec6c87%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-briefcase-men%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstuartandlau.com%252Fproducts%252Fthe-cary-briefcase-with-umbrella-holder-single-navy-and-tan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStuart%20%26amp%3B%20Lau%20Cary%20Single%20Briefcase%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20this).%20In%20short%2C%20a%20well-chosen%20briefcase%20never%20looks%20outdated%20when%20it%20matches%20your%20professional%20environment%2C%20and%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20timeless%20symbol%20of%20preparedness%20and%20professionalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-briefcase-men%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752785842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877fc7d3d5881a51c1d74cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-briefcase-men%22%2C%22summar