filiated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELavalock%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20great%20option.%20We%20checked%20with%20grilling%20experts%20who%20said%20that%20the%20smoke%20leak%20can%20happen%2C%20but%20the%20fire%20won't%20burn%20its%20way%20past%20the%20auger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20barbecue%20for%20a%20small%20group%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20too%20much%20or%20fuss%20with%20gadgetry%20or%20accessories%2C%20the%20Z%20Grills%20450B%20is%20a%20great%2C%20simple%2C%20and%20affordable%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8460ec8-71f5-44cc-833f-e87fc4ead149%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20splurge%5C%22%3EBest%20splurge%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20the%20most%20flawless%20barbecue%20with%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20effort%2C%20the%20Traeger%20Timberline%20series%20(go%20for%20the%20XL%20if%20you%20need%20the%20best%20pellet%20grill%20for%20large%20groups)%20is%20as%20good%20as%20it%20gets.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20you'll%20pay%20dearly%20for%20it%2C%20but%20purchasing%20a%20cover%20and%20taking%20cursory%20care%20will%20keep%20this%20grill%20going%20for%20many%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20be%20forewarned%20that%20the%20Timberline%20is%20exceptionally%20heavy%20at%20over%20250%20pounds.%20This%20is%20a%20true%20outdoor%20cooking%20station%2C%20minus%20a%20sink%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20something%20you'll%20want%20to%20cart%20around%20your%20backyard%2C%20but%20rather%20leave%20in%20place%20on%20a%20solid%20surface.%20Where%20a%20heavy-duty%20offset%20smoker%20with%20wagon%20wheels%20is%20your%20rough-and-ready%20all-terrain%20utility%20Jeep%2C%20the%20Timberline%20is%20more%20like%20a%20Cadillac.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVeteran%20grillers%20will%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20justify%20spending%20more%20than%20%243000%20on%20a%20pellet%20grill%2C%20especially%20one%20with%20relatively%20thin%20metal.%20This%20grill%20isn't%20for%20them%2C%20but%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20as%20hands-off%20and%20foolproof%20an%20experience%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20grill%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20keeping%20a%20steady%20temperature%20and%20cooking%20evenly%2C%20the%20metal%20on%20the%20firebox%20is%20surprisingly%20thin%2C%20especially%20compared%20with%20the%20quarter-inch-thick%20stuff%20you'll%20find%20on%20charcoal%20or%20stick-burning%20pit%20grills%20around%20the%20same%20price.%20Accessorizing%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20%24200%20purchase%20of%20a%20grill%20cover%2C%20is%20almost%20prohibitively%20expensive.%20Still%2C%20this%20is%20the%20best%20upgrade%20pellet%20grill%20of%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20that%20I've%20tried%2C%20and%20it's%20built%20to%20last%20better%20than%20any%20other%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Ftraeger-timberline-grill-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%20of%20the%20Traeger%20Timberline%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e0f0064-6a13-4f42-bf44-6f8bb6daf352%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20electric%5C%22%3EBest%20electric%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20market%20for%20pellet%20smokers%20to%20use%20indoors%20might%20be%20limited%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20there%20aren't%20any%20good%20choices.%20The%20GE%20Profile%20Smart%20Indoor%20Pellet%20Smoker%20is%20a%20reliable%20workhorse%2C%20able%20to%20infuse%20meat%20with%20smoky%20flavor%20without%20clouding%20up%20the%20house%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20active%20filtration%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20been%20using%20the%20countertop%20appliance%20for%20over%20a%20year%20with%20no%20regrets.%20Ribs%2C%20chicken%2C%20and%20pork%20meals%20have%20all%20come%20out%20tender%20and%20exactly%20as%20expected.%20The%20unit%20has%20a%20temperature%20range%20of%20150%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20to%20300.%20You%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20sear%20with%20this%20smoker%2C%20and%20it%20lacks%20any%20char%20from%20an%20outdoor%20wood-fire%20grill.%20Still%2C%20it's%20perfect%20for%20slow%20cooking%20and%20comes%20with%20various%20presets%20for%20different%20types%20of%20meat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221609%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20of%20brisket%20cooking%20in%20the%20GE%20Profile%20Smart%20Indoor%20Smoker%20and%20the%20finished%20product.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0decab1834fe31165bbb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221207%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrisket%20made%20in%20the%20GE%20smoker%20came%20out%20juicy%20and%20flavorful%2C%20albeit%20without%20a%20clear%20smoke%20ring.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20there's%20a%20major%20downside%2C%20it's%20that%20the%20smoker%20only%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20293%20square%20inches.%20Whenever%20I%20make%20a%20rack%20of%20ribs%2C%20I%20need%20to%20cut%20it%20in%20half%20so%20that%20it%20will%20fit.%20There%20are%20three%20removable%20trays%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20room%20that%20is%20available.%20The%20benefits%20this%20smoker%20offers%2C%20however%2C%20outweigh%20its%20limited%20size%20and%20hottest%20temperature%20capability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20an%20integrated%20temperature%20probe%20included%2C%20which%20will%20relay%20that%20info%20to%20the%20GE%20SmartHQ%20mobile%20app.%20With%20the%20app%2C%20you%20can%20also%20change%20the%20temperature%20and%20adjust%20the%20timer%20remotely.%20If%20you're%20into%20the%20smart%20stuff%2C%20the%20smoker%20is%20compatible%20with%20Alexa%20and%20Google%20Home.%20Since%20its%20debut%2C%20it's%20even%20come%20down%20in%20price%20to%20%24699%2C%20which%20might%20feel%20like%20an%20even%20better%20value%20come%20wintertime%2C%20when%20you%20can%20smoke%20a%20meal%20without%20trekking%20outside.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Tyler%20Hayes%2C%20contributor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fge-profile-smart-indoor-smoker-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGE%20Profile%20Smart%20Indoor%20Smoker%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d9800d3-17e3-4458-951d-b624572545c8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20charcoal%5C%22%3EBest%20charcoal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETending%20a%20charcoal%20fire%20is%20much%20easier%20said%20than%20done%2C%20and%20in%20almost%20every%20case%20of%20disappointing%20or%20failed%20grilling%20attempts%2C%20it%20is%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20downfall.%20Masterbuilt's%20towering%20Gravity%20Series%20is%20an%20imposing%20appliance%20with%20a%20large%20hopper%20and%20feeder%20that%2C%20thanks%20to%20WiFi%20connectivity%2C%20works%20just%20like%20a%20pellet%20smoker%2C%20but%20for%20charcoal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20go%20with%20charcoal%20over%20wood%20pellets%3F%20Many%20cooks%20argue%20that%20charcoal%20offers%20more%20flavor%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20a%20simple%20fact%20that%20charcoal%20burns%20much%2C%20much%20hotter%20than%20wood%20pellets.%20The%20Gravity%20Series%20ranges%20from%20about%20150%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20(a%20great%20temperature%20for%20low-and-slow%20smoking)%20up%20to%20about%20700%20degrees%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20for%20searing%20%E2%80%94%20something%20even%20the%20best%20pellet%20grills%20can't%20generally%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20it's%20a%20grill%2C%20griddle%2C%20and%20a%20(higher-temp)%20smoker%20all%20in%20one%2C%20earning%20the%20title%20of%20the%20best%20charcoal%20pellet%20grill.%20It%20also%20has%20two-sided%20cast-iron%20grates%2C%20with%20one%20thinner%20side%20dedicated%20to%20smoking%20and%20the%20thicker%20one%20for%20searing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20Masterbuilt%20Gravity%20Series%201050%20charcoal%20grill%20filled%20with%20hot%20dogs%2C%20hot%20dog%20buns%2C%20and%20more.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643829c85f081b0019c103ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20those%20wanting%20a%20smokier%20result%20than%20wood%20pellets%20produce%2C%20this%20is%20an%20easy%20and%20affordable%20way%20to%20achieve%20charcoal%20flavor%20and%20heat.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMonitoring%20the%20temperature%20with%20WiFi%20and%20Bluetooth%20was%20easy%2C%20and%20connectivity%20is%20about%20as%20steady%20as%20most%20grills%20we've%20tested%20%E2%80%94%20we%20couldn't%20go%20around%20the%20corner%20to%20the%20store%2C%20but%20we%20stayed%20connected%20around%20the%20house%2C%20adjusting%20temperature%20and%20even%20turning%20the%20grill%20off%20(though%20we%20recommend%20doing%20that%20in%20person).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Masterbuilt%20Gravity%20Series%20grill%20has%20a%20few%20downsides%20like%20any%20other.%20Firstly%2C%20it's%20made%20of%20relatively%20lightweight%20metal%2C%20which%20isn't%20good%20for%20heat%20retention%20or%20longevity%2C%20and%20secondly%2C%20it%20took%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20to%20build.%20Expectedly%2C%20temperatures%20tend%20to%20fluctuate%20more%20than%20they%20do%20in%20a%20wood-pellet%20smoker%2C%20but%20that's%20charcoal%20for%20you%20(briquettes%20will%20burn%20more%20evenly%20than%20hardwood%20lump).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e9149bd-c87b-47b7-ab10-5cffc6c59aa9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20choose%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20choose%20a%20pellet%20grill%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControls%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20increasing%20number%20of%20grills%20offer%20state-of-the-art%20WiFi%20or%20Bluetooth%20connectivity%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20monitor%20your%20brisket%20anywhere%20from%20your%20deck%20to%20miles%20away.%20However%2C%20some%20use%20simpler%20controls%20and%20don't%20require%20you%20to%20add%20another%20application%20to%20your%20phone.%20Tech%20gadgetry%20doesn't%20always%20correspond%20to%20better%20performance%2C%20so%20it's%20about%20your%20preference%20and%20cooking%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessories%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20of%20the%20best%20pellet%20smokers%20we%20tested%20don't%20offer%20a%20ton%20of%20extras%2C%20or%20the%20brands%20require%20you%20to%20purchase%20them%20separately.%20If%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20one-stop%20outdoor%20kitchen%20(minus%20the%20sink)%2C%20be%20prepared%20to%20spend%20more%20for%20a%20side%20burner%20and%20extra%20shelves.%20The%20Traeger%20Timberline%20and%20the%20Camp%20Chef%20Woodwind%20series%20have%20the%20most%20extra%20features%20of%20the%20grills%20we%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGrills%20are%20best%20measured%20in%20cooking%20surface%20area%2C%20usually%20in%20square%20inches%20of%20space.%20Smaller%20models%20in%20the%20450%20to%20575-square-inch%20range%20offer%20plenty%20of%20space%20for%20four%20to%20six%20people%2C%20and%20larger%20ones%2C%20above%20800%20square%20inches%2C%20can%20cook%20for%20roughly%20a%20dozen%20people%20or%20more.%20Look%20for%20the%20best%20pellet%20grill%20brands%20to%20show%20diagrams%20of%20their%20grill%20layouts%2C%20depicting%20how%20many%20pork%20shoulders%2C%20chicken%20wings%2C%20briskets%2C%20and%2For%20hamburger%20patties%20a%20grill%20can%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222887a740-79e4-4e23-ae45-8dfe86ff5a19%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20pellet%20grills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20pouring%20compressed%20wood%20pellets%20into%20the%20hopper%20of%20a%20Traeger%20Timberline%20XL%20Grill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63dd5e9ce33c4000193ae4bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221998%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMolly%20Allen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20more%20than%20two%20years%20building%20and%20testing%20pellet%20grills%20and%20smokers%2C%20speaking%20with%20experts%20like%20veteran%20TV%20host%20and%20author%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stevenraichlen.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteven%20Raichlen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fheygrillhey.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHey%20Grill%20Hey!%3C%2Fa%3E%20founder%20Susie%20Bulloch%2C%20and%20Chef%20Shola%20Olunloyo%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.studiokitchen.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStudio%20Kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20out%20what%20makes%20a%20good%20pellet%20grill%20and%20for%20whom%20they're%20made.%20We%20evaluated%20grills%20by%20cooking%20chicken%20drumsticks%20and%20pork%20shoulders%20%26quot%3Blow%20and%20slow%26quot%3B%20and%20grilling%20zucchini%20at%20a%20higher%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ETest%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EIdeal%20results%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EOur%20findings%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ETemperature%20control%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ESet%20target%20temperature%20and%20measure%20variance%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E5%20degrees%20or%20less%20away%20from%20target%20temperature%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EThe%20quality%20of%20heat%20retention%20generally%20increases%20with%20price%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ESmoking%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ELook%20for%20a%20smoke%20ring%20on%20bigger%20cuts%20of%20meat%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EDeep%20red%20rings%20and%20a%20noticeably%20smoky%20flavor%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ECharcoal%20grills%20or%20smokers%20will%20always%20produce%20smokier%20results%20than%20pellet%20smokers%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuild%20quality%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20considered%20the%20quality%20of%20materials%20as%20we%20built%20each%20grill%2C%20noting%20when%20metal%20was%20flimsier%20or%20more%20prone%20to%20denting.%20We%20also%20left%20each%20model%20out%20in%20the%20elements%20%E2%80%94%20some%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%20on%20end.%20None%20of%20the%20grills%20or%20the%20electronics%20we've%20tested%20have%20failed.%20Installing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110043315wj-20%26h%3Dc5a1c8e27416bae64c94e8caa2b3dc75e5b134a1b0df1c7df021bbd307e97cdf%26postID%3D687953362d2d32d710ee1458%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-pellet-smokers%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FLavalock-Nomex-gasket-smoker-stick%252Fdp%252FB00JO00S04%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equality%20gaskets%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20your%20own%20is%20a%20cheap%20and%20easy%20way%20to%20upgrade%20any%20grill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFrom%20building%20and%20connectivity%20to%20operating%20and%20cleaning%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20the%20process%20of%20owning%20and%20maintaining%20these%20grills.%20We%20considered%20if%20it%20was%20easy%20for%20a%20beginner%20to%20operate%20the%20grill%2C%20if%20the%20controls%20were%20intuitive%2C%20and%20if%20the%20setup%20process%20was%20unnecessarily%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20of%20the%20grills%20we%20tested%20came%20with%20limited%20accessories%2C%20some%20of%20them%20essential.%20While%20the%20budget-friendly%20pick%20on%20our%20list%20does%20come%20with%20a%20cover%20(that's%20survived%20two%20years%20outside)%2C%20every%20other%20grill%20we%20tested%20required%20a%20cover%20be%20purchased%20separately.%20Add%20on%20shelves%2C%20hooks%2C%20and%2For%20brackets%20that%20really%20should%20be%20included%2C%20and%20it%20gets%20expensive%20quickly.%20Still%2C%20build%20quality%20and%20warranty%20balanced%20out%20these%20pricier%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22927056c4-eac2-4e5a-a652-4a3529622816%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EPellet%20grill%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20Traeger%20Timberline%20Grill%20showing%20chicken%20drumsticks%20and%20pork%20being%20cooked.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F648cacdf51ea980019d6b04c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECleaning%20grills%20can%20be%20a%20pain%2C%20but%20a%20great%20workaround%20for%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20is%20a%20disposable%20aluminum%20tray%2C%20or%20lining%20the%20grill's%20catch%20pan%20with%20tin%20foil.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20pellet%20grill%20brand%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20hesitate%20to%20say%20one%20brand%20completely%20surpasses%20the%20rest%2C%20but%20Traeger%20grills%20and%20smokers%20routinely%20make%20the%20top%20of%20our%20lists.%20After%20testing%20grills%20from%20the%20Timberline%2C%20Ironwood%2C%20and%20Pro%20lines%2C%20we%20can%20confidently%20recommend%20almost%20any%20Traeger%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20the%20negatives%20of%20pellet%20grills%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20pellet%20grills%2C%20also%20known%20as%20pellet%20smokers%2C%20compare%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fthe-best-bbq-smoker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20barbecue%20smokers%3C%2Fa%3E%20favored%20by%20pitmasters%20or%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-charcoal-grill%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20charcoal%20grills%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20We%20asked%20Steven%20Raichlen%2C%20one%20of%20our%20favorite%20grillmasters%2C%20and%20he%20came%20back%20with%20a%20resounding%20%26quot%3BNo.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20did%20say%20that%20pellet%20smokers%20are%20great%20for%20the%20layperson%20who%20wants%20wood-smoke%20flavor%20without%20the%20associated%20sweat%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20a%20charcoal%20or%20wood%20pellet%20smoker%20better%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECharcoal%20gives%20a%20stronger%20flavor%2C%20but%20pellet%20smokers%20are%20far%20easier%20to%20use.%20It%20comes%20down%20to%20time%20and%20labor%20investment.%20Backyard%20grillers%20can%20excel%20with%20a%20pellet%20grill%2C%20while%20pit%20masters%20aren't%20likely%20to%20swap%20out%20their%20charcoal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20do%20buy%20a%20pellet%20smoker%2C%20don't%20expect%20the%20same%20smokiness%20in%20your%20food%20that%20you%20would%20if%20you%20delicately%20fed%20furniture-grade%2C%20kiln-dried%20cooking%20wood%20to%20an%20immaculately%20glowing%20bed%20of%20coals%20for%2012%20hours.%20That's%20the%20kind%20of%20art%20that%20can%20only%20and%20will%20only%20ever%20be%20done%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20pellet%20grills%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPellet%20grills%20have%20a%20hopper%20that%20feeds%20an%20auger%2C%20which%20grinds%20compressed%20hardwood%20pellets%20into%20smaller%20chunks%20that%20fall%20into%20and%20ignite%20in%20a%20firebox%2C%20creating%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPellet%20grill%20and%20pellet%20smoker%20can%20be%20used%20interchangeably.%20Grills%20tend%20to%20work%20with%20direct%20heat%2C%20while%20smokers%20often%20use%20indirect%20heat.%20Modern%20pellet%20grills%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20grills%20and%20smokers%20because%20they%20range%20between%20low-and-slow%20cooking%20temperatures%20(160-225%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20or%20so)%20and%20about%20500%20degrees%2C%20which%20is%20your%20average%20gas%20grill's%20highest%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20best%20pellets%20for%20smokers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pellet%20grill%20brand%20you%20buy%20will%20likely%20direct%20you%20to%20its%20own%20line%20of%20pellets%2C%20but%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20consider%20is%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Badditive-free%26quot%3B%20pellets.%20Lower-grade%20pellets%2C%20especially%20those%20without%20this%20distinction%2C%20can%20encompass%20a%20lot%20of%20impurities%20(down%20to%20even%20plastics%20and%20industrial%20scraps)%20because%20pellets%20are%20often%20forged%20from%20sawdust%20in%20commercial%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20type%20of%20wood%20you%20buy%20is%20highly%20subjective.%20Brands%20tend%20to%20recommend%20different%20blends%20or%20species%20of%20wood%20for%20different%20foods%2C%20though.%20Check%20out%20our%20full%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-smoker-pellets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20smoker%20pellets%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-pellet-smokers%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752783332000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64382f1a5f081b0019c1067c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-pellet-smokers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%20dozens%20of%20pellet%20grills%20and%20spoke%20to%20experts%20to%20find%20the%20best%20models%20for%20every%20budget%20and%20cooking%20style%2C%20from%20compact%20smokers%20to%20high-end%20picks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22oburke%40businessinsider.com%20(Owen%20Burke%2CTyler%20Hayes)