%3EHe%20laughs%20at%20the%20memory%20of%20those%20teenage%20years%2C%20single%E2%80%91handedly%20picking%20up%20skills%20like%20design%2C%20animation%2C%20and%20marketing%2C%20until%20he%20resembled%20%E2%80%9Ca%20one%E2%80%91man%20agency%2C%E2%80%9D%20juggling%20multiple%20roles.%20That%20hustle%20propelled%20him%20to%20a%20creative%20director%20post%20by%20the%20age%20of%2021%2C%20with%20a%20salary%20few%20could%20fathom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20crazy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20thought%20I%20had%20it%20all.%E2%80%9D%20But%20as%20he%20recounts%20the%20unrelenting%2015%20to%2016%E2%80%91hour%20days%2C%20the%20nights%20without%20sleep%2C%20the%20constant%20rush%20to%20meet%20deadlines%2C%20you%20begin%20to%20sense%20the%20cost%20of%20that%20very%20success.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20working%20through%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve%20alone%20in%20the%20office.%20My%20boss%20told%20me%20to%20take%20a%20break%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99ll%20rest%20when%20it%20is%20all%20done.%E2%80%99%20But%20that%20finish%20line%20kept%20moving.%20It%20was%20always%20just%20out%20of%20reach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20crash%20that%20changed%20everything%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20came%20the%20crash.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20hit%20a%20wall%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20voice%20steady%20but%20reflective.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367326%2Ftoxic-workplaces-solutions-healthy-workplace-work-life-balance-work-pressure-employee-wellbeing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurnout%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367326%2Ftoxic-workplaces-solutions-healthy-workplace-work-life-balance-work-pressure-employee-wellbeing%2F%5C%22%3Eis%20not%20just%20being%20tired%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20like%20breaking%20from%20the%20inside.%20I%20q