%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20eco-tourism%20model%20not%20only%20preserves%20biodiversity%20but%20also%20provides%20meaningful%20economic%20opportunities%20to%20the%20villagers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%202010%2C%20his%20conservation%20focus%20shifted%20towards%20Saraipung%20village.%20%E2%80%9CI%20chose%20Saraipung%20village%2C%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20inside%20the%20forest%20area%2C%20designated%20as%20a%20forest%20village%2C%20where%20I%20saw%20around%2010-15%20people%20entering%20the%20forest%20with%20bows%20and%20arrows%20in%20my%20initial%20visits%20to%20these%20jungles%20which%20was%20use%20to%20hunt%20wild%20animals%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20only%20three-four%20forest%20staffs%20were%20deputed%20to%20guard%20this%20huge%20jungle.%20I%20stepped%20in%20to%20do%20the%20conservation%20works%20involving%20the%20local%20youths%20for%20nature%20camps%20with%20other%20participants%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20Assam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20potential%20for%20change%2C%20he%20initiated%20conversations%20around%20environmental%20stewardship%2C%20emphasising%20the%20long-term%20benefits%20of%20conserving%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajib%20understood%20one%20crucial%20fact%20%E2%80%93%20the%20journey%20from%20hunting%20to%20conservation%20required%20more%20than%20harsh%20interdictions%3B%20it%20required%20empathy%20and%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20professor%20didn%E2%80%99t%20storm%20in%20with%20dicta%20from%20on%20high%3B%20rather%2C%20he%20made%20himself%20part%20of%20the%20community.%20He%20moved%20to%20the%20village%20for%20two%20months%20and%20became%20a%20fixture%20of%20their%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20installed%20an%20inverter%20on%20my%20personal%20jeep%20to%20project%20videos%20and%20visuals%20on%20wildlife%20conservation%20onto%20makeshift%20screens.%20Slowly%2C%20through%20these%20interactions%2C%20I%20helped%20envisage%20a%20future%20wit