gnificant%20income%20source%20for%20guides%20and%20homestay%20owners%20like%20Sanatan%20and%20Gokul.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestays%20have%20been%20developed%20and%20maintained%20by%20the%20villagers%20who%20have%20been%20trained%20to%20cater%20to%20tourists.%20Rajib%20shares%20that%20Saraipung%20village%20comprises%20about%20106%20households%2C%20with%20a%20population%20between%20300%20and%20400%20people.%20%E2%80%9CBeyond%20the%20direct%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F467748%2Fsustainable-homestay-dharamshala-kosen-rufu-mountain-retreat-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-tourism%20%3C%2Fa%3Eparticipants%2C%20many%20in%20the%20community%20contribute%20by%20preparing%20meals%2C%20maintaining%20homestays%2C%20and%20engaging%20visitors%20in%20cultural%20programs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanatan%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20homestay%20in%20Saraipung%20village%2C%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20villagers%20of%20Saraipung%20were%20engaged%20in%20hunting%20activities.%20When%20I%20was%20young%2C%20I%20would%20often%20accompany%20the%20other%20villagers%20on%20hunting%20trips.%20Rajib%20sir%20enlightened%20us%20on%20the%20negative%20impacts%20of%20hunting%20and%20introduced%20us%20to%20alternative%20means%20of%20sustenance.%20He%20frequently%20showed%20us%20short%20films%20on%20conservation%20and%20evem%20took%20us%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F466481%2Fassam-orang-national-park-mini-kaziranga-small-endangered-species%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOrang%2520National%2520Park%2520may%2520be%2CBengal%2520tiger%252C%2520and%2520pygmy%2520hog.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaziranga%20National%20Park%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20deepen%20our%20understanding%20of%20wildlife%2C%20conservation%2C%20and%20eco-friendly%20livelihoods%20such%20as%20running%20homestays.%E2%80